005package edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics;
006
007import edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics.proto.MecanumDriveMotorVoltagesProto;
008import edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics.struct.MecanumDriveMotorVoltagesStruct;
009import edu.wpi.first.util.protobuf.ProtobufSerializable;
010import edu.wpi.first.util.struct.StructSerializable;
011
012/** Represents the motor voltages for a mecanum drive drivetrain. */
013public class MecanumDriveMotorVoltages implements ProtobufSerializable, StructSerializable {
014  /** Voltage of the front left motor. */
015  public double frontLeftVoltage;
016
017  /** Voltage of the front right motor. */
018  public double frontRightVoltage;
019
020  /** Voltage of the rear left motor. */
021  public double rearLeftVoltage;
022
023  /** Voltage of the rear right motor. */
024  public double rearRightVoltage;
025
026  /** Constructs a MecanumDriveMotorVoltages with zeros for all member fields. */
027  public MecanumDriveMotorVoltages() {}
028
029  /**
030   * Constructs a MecanumDriveMotorVoltages.
031   *
032   * @param frontLeftVoltage Voltage of the front left motor.
033   * @param frontRightVoltage Voltage of the front right motor.
034   * @param rearLeftVoltage Voltage of the rear left motor.
035   * @param rearRightVoltage Voltage of the rear right motor.
036   */
037  public MecanumDriveMotorVoltages(
038      double frontLeftVoltage,
039      double frontRightVoltage,
040      double rearLeftVoltage,
041      double rearRightVoltage) {
042    this.frontLeftVoltage = frontLeftVoltage;
043    this.frontRightVoltage = frontRightVoltage;
044    this.rearLeftVoltage = rearLeftVoltage;
045    this.rearRightVoltage = rearRightVoltage;
046  }
047
048  @Override
049  public String toString() {
050    return String.format(
051        "MecanumDriveMotorVoltages(Front Left: %.2f V, Front Right: %.2f V, "
052            + "Rear Left: %.2f V, Rear Right: %.2f V)",
053        frontLeftVoltage, frontRightVoltage, rearLeftVoltage, rearRightVoltage);
054  }
055
056  /** MecanumDriveMotorVoltages struct for serialization. */
057  public static final MecanumDriveMotorVoltagesStruct struct =
058      new MecanumDriveMotorVoltagesStruct();
059
060  /** MecanumDriveMotorVoltages protobuf for serialization. */
061  public static final MecanumDriveMotorVoltagesProto proto = new MecanumDriveMotorVoltagesProto();
062}
